channel.description: Recent content on Hi, I'm Pulkit Komal

item.description: Hello, I am Pulkit, I have a degree in Computer Science & Engineering 👨‍🎓. I was born in Parramatta, Australia 🇦🇺 but I live in Ludhiana, India 🇮🇳 now. I love listening to music; my fav DJ is Marshmello 😎. My hobbies include watching anime [One Piece ❤️], reading books [Fiction 📖] & DIY. I am programmer 🧟‍♂️ & tech enthusiast 🤖. I intend to make a difference 😬.
